  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the binchotan grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Rinse the callaloo and pat dry with paper towels.",
    "Toss the callaloo with olive oil, garlic, salt, and tomato confit in a bowl.",
    "Place the callaloo on the preheated binchotan grill and roast for 8 minutes.",
    "Shake the grill to redistribute the callaloo and continue roasting for another 8 minutes.",
    "Remove the callaloo from the grill and garnish with parsley and lemon wedges.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
